headline: Agilent Announces CFO Transition
summary: SANTA CLARA, Calif., July 15, 2025--Agilent Technologies Inc. (NYSE: A) today announced that effective July 31, Senior Vice President and Chief Financial Officer Bob McMahon will step down from his role as he relocates to the East Coast for family reasons and prepares for the next chapter in his career.
